{"tid":47893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張小明香港出席活動！！！","createTime":"2016-12-20T16:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T18:21:12.000Z","uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db5ff2a645d4d3fc82c3bd2f1b8bf03d9e56f29c","tid":47893,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:23:45.000Z","msg":"多日未在香港公開露面的中聯辦主任張曉明，參加外交部駐港特派員公署舉行的新春酒會。 <br />\n<br />\n外交部駐港特派員公署的官方網頁上載一張酒會的相片。除張曉明，行政長官梁振英，政務司司長林鄭月娥，署理財政司司長陳家強和立法會主席梁君彥等都有出席。 <br />\n<br />\n今次是梁振英表明不競逐連任後，與張曉明首次同場出席活動。張曉明之前在北京出席中央經濟工作會議。"},{"pid":"d4f8529dd98b4049fb73213bfa7b666e3869896e","tid":47893,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:25:02.000Z","msg":"仲落到番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52690ef0f7c924eaeccbe5fc3347a855568d02cd","tid":47893,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:30:27.000Z","msg":"又要俾幾多時間刁總<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f45f7fdcabda201eeade9d9f353f64dc1f0829","tid":47893,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:42:13.000Z","msg":"屌仲以為佢玩撚完"},{"pid":"f067ad76a373ce8aa989274a3b87e96769498905","tid":47893,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:44:33.000Z","msg":"成報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbca7ac987a918060398d6196377a29fe23e3ec8","tid":47893,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:01:26.000Z","msg":"仲以為成報批中咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0ea2b899fdb888e7a824346c3e37e64d37dceb","tid":47893,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T19:01:42.000Z","msg":"呢鋪成報點解釋？"},{"pid":"9e3caf9956cd166989bba9bc05b646ffde848d3f","tid":47893,"uid":42611,"like":0,"dislike"